# RMK - TransitGo — Cursor Rules

## Project Identity
  - App Name: RMK - TransitGo
    - Type: React Native mobile app(Expo SDK 51 +)
      - Purpose: Campus bus tracking system for RMK College
        - Roles: Student, Driver, Admin
          - Backend: Supabase ONLY(Auth + Postgres + Realtime)

---

## Non - Negotiable Backend Rules
  - ALWAYS use `@supabase/supabase-js` for ALL data operations
    - NEVER use localStorage, AsyncStorage as a database substitute, in -memory arrays as persistent state, or any mock / fake backend
      - ALL auth must go through `supabase.auth.signUp()` and`supabase.auth.signInWithPassword()`
        - ALL data reads / writes must use`supabase.from('table').select/insert/update/delete()`
          - ALL real - time features must use `supabase.channel().on('postgres_changes', ...)` subscriptions
            - Supabase client lives in `lib/supabase.ts` and is imported everywhere — never re - initialised

---

## Project Structure
  ```
app/
  (auth)/
    welcome.tsx        ← role selection screen
    student-auth.tsx   ← student sign in / sign up
    driver-auth.tsx    ← driver sign in / sign up
    admin-auth.tsx     ← admin sign in
  (student)/
    index.tsx          ← home: map + wait for me
    schedule.tsx       ← route stops + ETAs
    profile.tsx        ← student profile + sign out
  (driver)/
    index.tsx          ← trip control + alert panel
    route.tsx          ← assigned route + stops
    profile.tsx        ← driver profile + sign out
  (admin)/
    index.tsx          ← fleet management
    routes.tsx         ← route + stop management
    logs.tsx           ← trip history logs
lib/
  supabase.ts          ← supabase client (single source of truth)
  types.ts             ← all TypeScript interfaces
constants/
  theme.ts             ← all colors, fonts, spacing
```

---

## Design System(Follow Exactly — Cityflo - Inspired)

### Colors(from constants / theme.ts)
  ```ts
export const Colors = {
  primary:    '#F5C518',   // yellow — highlight actions
  dark:       '#1A1A1A',   // near black — primary CTA buttons, text
  bg:         '#FAFAF8',   // off-white — screen background
  surface:    '#FFFFFF',   // white — cards
  border:     '#EEEEEE',   // dividers
  textPrimary:'#111111',   // main text
  textSecond: '#888888',   // secondary/label text
  green:      '#22C55E',   // active/live/accept states
  red:        '#EF4444',   // deny/end/cancel states
  amber:      '#F59E0B',   // warnings / no-response state
  blue:       '#3B82F6',   // student ping dot on map
}
```

### Typography
  - Body font: `DM Sans`(via`@expo-google-fonts/dm-sans`)
    - Mono font: `DM Mono`(via`@expo-google-fonts/dm-mono`) — use for bus numbers, plates, times, IDs
      - Never use system fonts(no Arial, Roboto, San Francisco defaults)

### Component Rules
  - Card border - radius: `20px`
    - Button border - radius: `14px`
      - Input border - radius: `12px`
        - Card shadow: `{ shadowColor:'#000', shadowOffset:{width:0,height:2}, shadowOpacity:0.07, shadowRadius:8, elevation:3 }`
          - Primary CTA button: dark background(`#1A1A1A`) + white text + bold
            - Highlight button: yellow(`#F5C518`) + black text + bold
              - All screens: off - white(`#FAFAF8`) background
                - Map: OpenStreetMap tiles — `urlTemplate="https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png"`

